sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Extension UI
    participant CR as Crypto Module
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as SQLite Database

    Note over U,DB: Save Credential Flow
    U->>UI: Enter site, username, and password
    UI->>CR: Encrypt plaintext password with master key
    CR-->>UI: Return AES-256-GCM encrypted_password
    UI->>API: POST /credentials with JWT and encrypted payload
    API->>API: Verify JWT token
    API->>DB: Insert credential for authenticated user
    DB-->>API: Insert success
    API-->>UI: 201 Created
    UI-->>U: Show success toast

    Note over U,DB: Retrieve Credential Flow
    U->>UI: Open Passwords tab
    UI->>API: GET /credentials with JWT
    API->>API: Verify JWT token
    API->>DB: Query credentials by user_id
    DB-->>API: Return encrypted credentials list
    API-->>UI: 200 OK + encrypted credentials
    UI-->>U: Display credential list

    U->>UI: Click Show on one credential
    UI->>CR: Decrypt encrypted_password with master key
    CR-->>UI: Plaintext password
    UI-->>U: Reveal password temporarily
